    <item>
      <title>信用恐惧量规会恶化，因为关税问题抵消了软CPI</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/credit-fear-gauges-worsen-as-tariff-concerns-offset-soft-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当投资者担心关税的经济影响时，人们对公司信贷违约的担忧升级，即使美国通货膨胀数据在新税前表明消费者有所缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/credit-fear-gauges-worsen-as-tariff-concerns-offset-soft-cpi</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 13:05:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国经济：核心CPI的增长少于3月的预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/us-economy-core-cpi-rises-less-than-expected-in-march-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三月份，美国消费者的价格降低了，因为所谓的核心消费者价格指数上涨了0.1％，最少九个月。同时，每周失业者的索赔要求估计为223,000，而持续的索赔则下降了43,000。迈克尔·麦基（Michael McKee）在彭博电视台上报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/us-economy-core-cpi-rises-less-than-expected-in-march-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 12:48:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顾问说，德国经济将在2025年停滞不前关税。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/german-institutes-slash-2025-outlook-and-warn-of-tariff-pain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国领先的研究机构称，今年德国经济不会看到有意义的增长，唐纳德·特朗普的关税政策威胁到一个平淡无奇的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/german-institutes-slash-2025-outlook-and-warn-of-tariff-pain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通货膨胀提升的呼吁，国债反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/treasuries-chaos-is-triggering-aftershocks-across-global-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在上个月美国通货膨胀率意外涨势之后，国库会获得了债券交易者，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）不断发展的贸易政策动摇了债券交易者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/treasuries-chaos-is-triggering-aftershocks-across-global-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 01:43:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股票在五年内随着特朗普关税缓刑而跳高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/european-stock-futures-jump-after-trump-unveils-tariff-reprieve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）停止计划对数十个贸易伙伴实施较高互惠关税的计划之后的第二天，欧洲股票汇集起来，这使人们对全球贸易战的潜在损害造成的疑问减轻了担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/european-stock-futures-jump-after-trump-unveils-tariff-reprieve</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 00:49:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于贸易战的市场担忧持续存在，石油恢复损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者评估了美国贸易政策的突然转变，石油扩大了动荡的运行，在周三的救济集会后，期货恢复了损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 23:25:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>期货由于CPI未能平息经济焦虑：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来购买最大的购买量最大，即使在通货膨胀数据延长了国债的反弹之后，风险的胃口在华尔街消失了。 S＆amp; P 500准备在周三激增的大约20％的激增中追溯，因为投资者为全球贸易敌意的潜在持久时期做好了准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 22:44:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
